<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_View_Helper_FormElement::_getInfo() method is unsetting the id and next the helper method, eg. Zend_View_Helper_FormCheckbox::formCheckbox() is not setting the id, so setting id for checkbox and radio elements is not possible.</p>

<p>It could be fixed by adding this line after setting the name, and before setting the value:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code> 
. ' id="' . htmlspecialchars($id, ENT_COMPAT, 'UTF-8') . '"'
</code></pre>

